name: Verifying Talent Module Functionalities for Invlaid Login Credentials

elements.name: Verify that the talent is not able to login using invalid credentials.

steps.name: Application is launched in "Release" Environment
I am logged in as "Talent" using the "agreen" and "Mbo.2012"
Verify that message saying Invalid Username or Password is displayed.

elements.name: Verify talent is able to see 5 tabs in landing page

steps.name: Application is launched in "Release" Environment
I am logged in as "Talent" using the "agreen" and "Mbo.2011"
I am in "Talent" landing page
I will see "5" tabs present
Those Tabs are "Shared With Me","Shown Interest", "Bookmarked", "Saved Search Results","All Opportunities"
I will see sort by option available with in every tab

elements.name: Verify talent is able to see shared opportunities under 'Shared With Me' tab

steps.name: I click on "Shared With Me" tab
I will see total count of opportunity cards shared with me
I will see count of opportunities
I will see the Opportunity Name
I will see the Company logo
I will see the Posted date of Opportunity in Month DD YYYY
I will see Location, Bill Rate, Start date and End date

elements.name: Verify that the MBO Partners logo is present, and it navigates to the opportunity listing page

steps.name: I will see the Company logo
I am in "Talent" landing page

elements.name: Verify that the footer is present and have the MBO Copyright signature, Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.

steps.name: The footer should be present on the bottom of the page
The footer should contain the MBO Copyright signature with the current year
The footer should contain a Privacy Policy hyperlink and it should navigate to the right page
The footer should contain Terms of Use hyperlink and it should navigate to the right page

elements.name: Verify that there is an option to filter the opportunities listed.

steps.name: Verify that Talent should have options to filter the opportunities.
Verify that The filter should have options Project Date,Client,Bill Rate,Location,Skills
